name: MARS (DRC-20)
description: The MARS token celebrates Elon Musk's daring spirit in exploring Mars and pays homage to the first space mission funded by Dogecoin. As the Cardinals protocol looks to the future with unwavering determination, it embodies the revolutionary ideals dear to Elon Musk. MARS DRC-20 will propel you through a cosmic journey between dream and reality, discovering numerous mysteries...
